S.FORM: Mikhail Mishustin u siwkay niza u pilecuhan ni Mikhail Mishustin i Lobnya . nalecuhan ciniza i 3 a bulad 3 a demiad 1966 a mihcaan. pahezekay niza i tabakiay a cacudadan nu Moscow (Moscow State Technological University ). micakat u cunli ( Prime Minister) nu Russia ayza sa ci Mikhail Mishustin , micakat a demiad sa i 2020 a mihcaan 1 bulad 16 demiad. u ngangan niza u sulit tu ngangan nu Russia a kamu:Mikhail Mishustin u sulit tu ngangan nu hulam a kamu: u sulit tu ngangan nu Sakizaya a kamu:Mihayiel Misusecin u sapuyaay a kakuniza kakuniza malalitin tu ihekalay atu zumaay a natinengan List of current heads of state and government Mikhail Mishustin
